i-MSCP RemoteBridge plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.8
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        - Fixed: Domain update was not working with Domains created by i-MSCP Panel
		- update is now only updating domain related things
		- removed unneded code
		- action renamed to update_dmn
	- Renamed: action for adding mails are now 'add_mail'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.7
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

        - Add: Add mailaccount for mailbox and/or forwarding
                - action 'addmail'
			- adds mailaddress (mailbox and/or forwarding)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.6
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Add: User list 
		- action 'get'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Add: Update user and domain
		- action 'update'

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Fixed: Disabled items must not be counted by the getCountRequests() method
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Fixed: Column domain_created_id has been removed from i-MSCP core

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	- Small fixes

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2013-11-18: Sascha Bay
